com.example.yudyang.regulus.core.antlr4

Interface ElasticsearchParserListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ElasticsearchParserBaseListener

    public interface ElasticsearchParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by ElasticsearchParser.
